Release Notes for Solace PubSub+ for Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF).

### v2.1.0

**Release Date: September 14, 2018**

This minor release contains an upgrade to Solace PubSub+ message broker v8.12.0.1007 and the following:

* Adds free Solace PubSub+ Standard edition message broker with new plans.
* Adds Credhub support which is available from PCF v2.x.x
* Adds a new orphaned resource policy.
* Supports optional username parameter at bind time.
* Removes support for PCF v1.12.x
* Adds support for PCF v2.3.x
* Supports upgrades from Solace PubSub+ for PCF release v2.0.x
* Supports upgrades from Solace PubSub+ for PCF enterprise evaluation tile to the enterprise tile.

### v2.0.2

**Release Date: August 3, 2018**

The releases addresses an authentication configuration defect which can expose internal admin credentials. Additional security checks are added to the errand.
The bundled Solace PubSub+ message broker is v8.11.0.1033.

### v2.0.1

**Release Date: July 27, 2018**

This minor release contains an upgrade to Solace PubSub+ message broker v8.11.0.1033.

### v2.0.0

**Release Date: July 11, 2018**

This major release contains Solace PubSub+ message broker v8.11.0.1029 and the following:

* As a major and renamed release, upgrades from older named product solace-messaging to solace-pubsub are not possible. It will be possible to upgrade from Solace PubSub+ for PCF v2.0.0 to subsequent releases.
* Product rebranding from solace-messaging to solace-pubsub+ along with renamed plans.
* Addition of configurable options for MySQL (internal, as a marketplace service, external )
* Test errand accepts self-signed certs
* Removing support for PCF v1.11.x
* Removal of support for the “Community Plan” service plan.

### v1.4.0

**Release Date: April 13, 2018**

This release contains VMR v8.9.0.1008 and the following:

